      "patchset_number": 5,
      "message": "tested & working fine. \nAPI is now aligned with March 2024 version of O-RAN R1-AP spec for A1-Policy management. Except for: \n* Additional optional parameters added to several calls, and severaladditional operations not in the spec. \n* Bug in getpolicyTypes & getPolicies operations, where an array is required instead of single object. (To be fixed in July spec version) \n* Policy Type added to createPolicy operation (bug is spec) (to be fixed in July spec version) \n* Status notifications callbacks cannot be registered correctly. (Updates coming in July spec version)",
